---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Questor's Invitational -Quest Labs">

<div class="prog-page">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="prog-hero">
  <div class="prog-hero-bg"></div>
  <p class="prog-hero-eyebrow">Futures Literacies Invitational Playground</p>
  <h1 class="prog-hero-title prog-hero-title--flip">FLIP</h1>
  <p class="prog-hero-subtitle">The Questor's Invitational</p>
  <p class="prog-hero-sub">A 12-week creative & futures journey.<br>You're invited to meet your future Self.</p>
  <div class="prog-hero-cta">
    <a href="#cohort" class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary">Join a Cohort →</a>
    <a href="#journey" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost cta-secondary">Explore the Arc</a>
    <a href="#tiers" class="cta-ghost">Choose Your Path</a>
  </div>
  <div class="prog-scroll-hint">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="prog-scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- WHAT IS THIS -->
<section id="what" style="padding: 5rem 2.5rem; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <div class="prog-reveal">
    <p class="prog-section-label">The Premise</p>
    <h2 class="prog-section-title">Somewhere between 2026 and 2032,<br>there is a <em>portal</em>.</h2>

    <p class="prog-section-body">
      We’re crossing a threshold into the unknown...<br><br>
      ...but don’t lose hope.<br><br>
      🤫 A whisper of wisdom from beyond?<br><br>
      Remember, someone built this world.<br><br>
      We’re here to build a new one. 🌍<br><br>
      Over 12 weeks, a cohort of 6 brave travelers move through 12 worlds. Each week the world changes: same crew, different questions. We keep what serves our future Self and collective. We discover what we’re building toward.<br><br>
      By the final session, each traveler holds a <strong style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">2032 Job Description</strong> assembled piece by piece across 12 weeks of Artists Way practices and Sandbox Sessions.<br><br>
      Not a resume. A living document. Equal parts manifesto, methodology, and spell.
    </p>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid #6B3FA0; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; background: rgba(107,63,160,0.06);">
      <p style="font-size:14px; color:#C4A8E8; margin:0 0 0.5rem; font-style:italic;">Teaching? Leading a school?</p>
      <a href="/educators" class="bridge-link" style="font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:#C4A8E8; text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid currentColor; padding-bottom:2px;">Flip the Script is built specifically for educators and school leaders →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EARTH DAY LAUNCH + NEXT COHORT -->
<div class="prog-earthday-section" id="cohort">
  <div class="prog-earthday-inner">

    <div class="prog-earthday-top prog-reveal">
      <div class="prog-earth-orb">🌍</div>
      <div class="prog-earthday-headline">
        <p class="prog-section-label">Cohort 01 · Founding</p>
        <h2 class="prog-section-title" style="text-align:left;">Launched<br><em>Earth Day.</em></h2>
        <div class="prog-cohort-full-notice" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
          <span>The founding cohort is full and in motion.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-next-ctas prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- COHORT 02 WAITLIST -->
<div class="prog-waitlist-section" id="waitlist">
  <div class="prog-waitlist-inner prog-reveal">
    <p class="prog-waitlist-eyebrow">Cohort 02 · Now Forming</p>
    <h2 class="prog-waitlist-heading">Your spot is waiting.</h2>
    <p class="prog-waitlist-body">Cohort 02 opens after the founding cohort completes. Add your name now. You'll be first through the door, before it opens publicly.</p>

    <form class="prog-waitlist-form" id="waitlistForm" name="cohort-02-waitlist" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="cohort-02-waitlist" />
      <input class="prog-waitlist-input" type="text" name="name" placeholder="your name" required />
      <input class="prog-waitlist-input" type="email" name="email" placeholder="your email" required />
      <textarea class="prog-waitlist-input prog-waitlist-textarea" name="navigating" rows="3" placeholder="what are you navigating right now?"></textarea>
      <button class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary prog-waitlist-submit" type="submit">Reserve my spot in Cohort 02 →</button>
    </form>

    <div class="prog-waitlist-confirm" id="waitlistConfirm" style="display:none;">
      <p class="prog-waitlist-confirm-msg">You're on the list. We'll find you when the portal opens. In the meantime, the Sandbox Sessions are open. Come play.</p>
      <a href="https://lu.ma/questlabs" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find a Sandbox Session →</a>
    </div>

    <p class="prog-waitlist-note">No commitment. Just your name at the threshold.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS CAROUSEL -->
<div class="prog-testimonials-section">
  <div class="prog-testimonials-carousel">
    <div class="prog-testimonials-track">

      <blockquote class="prog-testimonial-slide">
        <p class="prog-testimonial-quote">"She was really supportive of my practice, never pushing me further than I wanted to go but advising me and reassuring me about how I was progressing. She really helped me get back on track, holding my hand just enough along the way."</p>
        <cite class="prog-testimonial-cite">— Clare, returning to a personal practice</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <blockquote class="prog-testimonial-slide">
        <p class="prog-testimonial-quote">"She's not only listening to what you're saying verbally, but she's also listening to your tone, your word choice — she's able to develop a more well-informed understanding of your state and situation. Makēda has been an invaluable source of support for me."</p>
        <cite class="prog-testimonial-cite">— Stephanie, building a music career</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <blockquote class="prog-testimonial-slide">
        <p class="prog-testimonial-quote">"By asking the right questions, providing the right tools, and being very supportive, Makēda helped me succeed in my academic studies, personal life, and with a difficult transition towards my professional life. Today I am much happier."</p>
        <cite class="prog-testimonial-cite">— Etienne, navigating a life transition</cite>
      </blockquote>

    </div>
    <div class="prog-t-controls">
      <button class="prog-t-btn" id="progPrev" aria-label="Previous">←</button>
      <div class="prog-t-dots" id="progDots"></div>
      <button class="prog-t-btn" id="progNext" aria-label="Next">→</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- TIERS -->
<div class="prog-tiers-section" id="tiers">
  <div class="prog-tiers-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">How deep do you want to dive?</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">You'll meet the future<br><em>regardless</em>.</h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">Choose your level of participation. All three tiers get to peek into the future.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prog-tiers-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-witness">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🌱</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Witness</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Good -I'm interested</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">4</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">milestone sessions</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Weeks 1 · 4 · 8 · 12 &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~3 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Milestone moments of the journey</li>
          <li>Final ceremony & Job Description reveal</li>
          <li>Access to session recordings</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">Perfect if your time is limited →</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-traveler">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🔥</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Traveler</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Better -I want the arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">8</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, every other week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Alternating weeks &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~5-6 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Full arc in compressed form</li>
          <li>Partial 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Beta feedback role</li>
          <li>Dyad partnerships</li>
          <li>Black Menagerie archetype practice</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">The full story, every other chapter →</div>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-questor">
        <span class="prog-tier-icon">🌟</span>
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Questor</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Best -I'm all in</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">12</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, full arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Every week &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~7-8 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Complete 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Co-creator of the methodology</li>
          <li>Testimonial & credit in future launches</li>
          <li>Morning pages + Artist Dates practice</li>
          <li>Full Black Menagerie archetype rotation</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="prog-tier-cta">Build the world from inside it →</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- <div class="prog-reveal" style="margin-top:2rem;transition-delay:0.3s">
      <div style="background:rgba(69,49,96,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(139,116,171,0.15);padding:1.5rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B74AB;margin-bottom:0.3rem;">When & Where</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.95rem;color:rgba(240,236,248,0.75);">7:30pm Berlin &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8:30pm Durban &nbsp;·&nbsp; 1:30pm New York</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(240,236,248,0.35);margin-top:0.2rem;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;">90 min · Zoom · Recorded within 24hrs</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> -->
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

